<LegalPage heading="Shipping & Returns">
  <h2>Shipping</h2>
  <p>We deliver all orders within <strong>7 to 10 working days from the date of purchase.</strong> If you have any questions or concerns about your shipment, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:info@mirkash.com">info@mirkash.com</a>.</p>
  <p><strong>Delivery to India</strong><br />All prices include GST, and we offer free shipping across India.</p>
  <p><strong>International Orders</strong><br />For deliveries outside India, please visit <a href="https://www.mirkash.com">www.mirkash.com</a>. If you need further assistance, our support team is here to help.</p>

  <h2>Return &amp; Refund</h2>
  <p>If sadly, you do not love your purchase, we will happily <strong>accept returns within 15 days</strong> of receiving your order. For any return-related inquiries, please email <a href="mailto:info@mirkashco.com">info@mirkashco.com</a>.</p>
  <p>To qualify for a return, please ensure the product is unused, in resalable condition, and packed in its original packaging&mdash;including the dust bag and the Mir Kash box.</p>
  <p>Please note: Return shipping and any related duties are the responsibility of the customer. Mir Kash does not cover return shipping costs.</p>
  <p>When returning, kindly send your product and shipment details to <a href="mailto:info@mirkashco.com">info@mirkashco.com</a>. Once your return is approved, we will process your refund within 14 days, credited back to your original payment method.</p>
</LegalPage>
